-- MOVES-Jardine Lloyd Thompson names Jim Pierce chairman of U.S. specialty business
-- 
-- Wed Sep 10, 2014 03:04PM EDT
-- None



Sept 10 (Reuters) - Insurance broker Jardine Lloyd Thompson Group Plc <JLT.L> named Jim Pierce chairman of its new JLT Specialty Insurance Services Inc in the United States.

Prior to this, Pierce was chairman of Marsh's Global Industry Practices. The company also appointed Michael Rice chief executive and Patrick Donnelly as president and deputy CEO of its U.S. specialty operations last week.